Paytm Insider: This is huge for independent music and club gigs in India. You can join their affiliate program through an Indian affiliate network called Cuelinks (which currently offers around 2.2% commission per sale for Insider).

BookMyShow: They host larger EDM festivals (like Sunburn). You can promote their events using affiliate networks like EarnKaro or Cuelinks.

SkillBox: This is arguably the most important platform for your niche. SkillBox is the go-to ticketing partner for deep underground techno, trance, and indie events in India. While they may not have a public affiliate link network like Paytm Insider, once your site is live, you can reach out to them directly for a partnership.